These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, rat, hamster, fish
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, emerald, orange, white
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
5. the person who likes white is between the person who likes emerald and the person who likes orange##2
6. the owner of the fish is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Pet   | fish | mouse     | hamster | rat |
| Color     | purple     | orange | white  | emerald      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, western, martial-arts, documentary
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, aconite, dahlia, lily
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | western    | documentary     | martial-arts  |
| Flower     | daisy    | dahlia | aconite | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, taxi, trike, bus
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, journalist, freelancer, entrepreneur
1. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
2. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
3. the freelancer is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the architect is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
5. the freelancer is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Transport   | taxi   | trike   | roller  | bus |
| Job           | journalist | entrepreneur | freelancer | architect  |

