.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, bird, guinea-pig
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, chestnut, red, orange
1. the person who likes orange is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the cat and the person who likes red##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Pet         | frog | cat | guinea-pig | bird  |
| Color   | chestnut  | emerald   | orange  | red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, backgammon, domino
There 4 different types of food: apple, spinach, zucchini, peas
1. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing chess##1
5. the person eating peas is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Game   | chess    | bridge   | backgammon | domino    |
| Food      | spinach | apple | zucchini       | peas |

