.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, siglo, vegafina, dunhill
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, techno, hip-hop, gospel
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of gospel and the vegafina-smoker##2
3. the fan of d&b is between the fan of hip-hop and the oliveros-smoker##2
4. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Cigar    | oliveros | vegafina | dunhill | siglo |
| Music-Genre   | techno | d&b  | hip-hop    | gospel  |

