.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, horror, action, romance
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, dog, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person watching action movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching romance movies##2
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the dog and the person watching romance movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | romance | action | horror     |
| Pet     | mouse | cat  | guinea-pig   | dog |

