.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, pony, rabbit
4 different games are played: go, domino, monopoly, billiard
1. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing domino##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
6. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Pet         | rabbit | pony | cat | goat   |
| Game   | domino | monopoly | go      | billiard |

