.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cherry, artichoke, grapefruit
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, poker, backgammon
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
3. the person playing backgammon is the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
5. the person eating spinach is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating cherry is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Food     | spinach | cherry   | artichoke      | grapefruit      |
| Game   | scrabble     | poker | monopoly | backgammon |

