.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, trike, subway
City: rome, san-francisco, london, prague
1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person driving the trike is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
3. the person driving the tram is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Transport   | car | tram | trike      | subway   |
| City   | london  | san-francisco    | rome | prague |

