.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, tea, cola
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, poker, billiard
1. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing billiard is the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
6. the person playing poker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage       | lemonade | tea | cola    | juice      |
| Game   | poker       | billiard       | scrabble | monopoly |

