.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, gospel, d&b, disco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, sprite, soy-milk
1. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
2. the fan of pop is the fan of pop##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
5. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop | d&b  | disco | gospel |
| Beverage           | sprite     | soy-milk | mirinda    | tea     |

