.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, magic-tricks, photography, drawing
City: london, liverpool, hannover, marseilles
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | rock-climbing | drawing  | photography      |
| City    | marseilles | london | hannover | liverpool |

