The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, martial-arts, fantasy, romance
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, siglo, dunhill, bongani
1. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is the bongani-smoker##1
4. the siglo-smoker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
6. the dunhill-smoker is the person watching musical movies##1
7. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts | romance | fantasy | musical |
| Cigar   | bongani     | alhambra       | siglo   | dunhill      |

