The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, writing, gardening
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Game      | canasta | whist    | domino  | poker |
| Hobby   | chess       | filmmaking | writing | gardening  |

