.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, game, chaman, pall-mall
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, argentine, indian
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is the indian##1
3. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the argentine is between the pall-mall-smoker and the indian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Cigar   | chaman | game  | old-henry  | pall-mall |
| Nationality           | indonesian    | indian | argentine | colombian |

