The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, filmmaking, magic-tricks, traveling
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family        | spy       | drama   | documentary |
| Hobby    | traveling | magic-tricks | filmmaking | woodworking  |

