.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, nigerian, mexican, german
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, indie, electronic, classical
1. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
2. the fan of classical is the fan of classical##1
3. the german is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of d&b is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the dutch##1
7. the mexican is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Nationality   | nigerian     | dutch     | mexican          | german |
| Music-Genre      | d&b | indie | classical | electronic  |

 